<HEADLINE> Sunday's TV News Show Lineup  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	Lineup for the Sunday TV news shows:  

</P>
<P>
	ABC's ``This Week'' -- Topic: Kosovo. Guests: Balkans envoy  
Richard Holbrooke, Sens. Richard Lugar, R-Ind., and Chuck Robb, 
D-Va.; and Vuk Draskovic, Yugoslav deputy prime minister. 

</P>
<P>
                              *------	 

</P>
<P>
	CBS' ``Face the Nation'' -- Topic: Kosovo. Guests: Sens. John  
McCain, R-Ariz.; Richard Shelby, R-Ala., and Joseph Lieberman, 
D-Conn.; Sandy Berger, national security adviser; and Karen Abu 
Zayd, U.S. representative to the United Nations High Commission on 
Refugees. 

</P>
<P>
                              *------	 

</P>
<P>
	NBC's ``Meet the Press'' -- Topics: Kosovo and baseball. Guests:  
Secretary of State Albright, Yugoslav U.N. Ambassador Vladislaf 
Jovanovic, Sens. Chuck Hagel, R-Neb., and James Inhofe, R-Okla.; 
and Mark McGwire of the St. Louis Cardinals. 

